# Role: engagement-engineer

> **Owns:** Comments (CRUD on published articles, owner-only edit/delete) and Likes (idempotent toggle, count aggregation).
> Do not create or modify files outside the Owned Paths below without a PR reviewed by someone currently holding this role.

## Role Charter
You own the two lightweight social-interaction features on articles. Both are small, well-bounded pieces — the discipline here is strict ownership checks and idempotency, not complexity.

## Owned Paths
```
src/controllers/commentController.ts
src/controllers/likeController.ts
src/services/commentService.ts
src/services/likeService.ts
src/repositories/commentRepository.ts
src/repositories/likeRepository.ts
src/routes/commentsRoutes.ts   (sub-router mounted under articles)
src/routes/likesRoutes.ts      (sub-router mounted under articles)
